       S3100-READ-FILE-RTN.

           INITIALIZE       WK-AREA
                            WK-HOST-OUT
                            OT-REC

           READ  IN-FILE     AT  END
            SET  IN-EOF-Y    TO  TRUE
           END-READ

           EVALUATE  WK-IN-F-ST
               WHEN  ZERO
               WHEN  CO-CHA-04
                     ADD   CO-NUM-1    TO  WK-AC-READ-CNT
170224*              고객식별자
                     MOVE  IN-CUST-IDNFR
                       TO  WK-CUST-IDNFR
170224*              모기업법인고객식별자
                     MOVE  IN-MAMA-CC-CUST-IDNFR
                       TO  WK-MAMA-CC-CUST-IDNFR

               WHEN  CO-CHA-10
                     SET   IN-EOF-Y    TO  TRUE
               WHEN  OTHER
                     MOVE 'IN-FILE OPEN ERROR : FILE-ST IS '
                                       TO  XZUGEROR-I-MSG
                     MOVE  WK-IN-F-ST  TO  XZUGEROR-I-MSG(34:2)
                     #ERROR  CO-EBM02001 CO-UBM02001 WK-IN-F-ST
                     #OKEXIT CO-CHA-08
           END-EVALUATE

           IF FUNCTION MOD(WK-AC-READ-CNT, 100000) = CO-NUM-0
              #USRLOG 'WK-AC-READ-CNT : ' WK-AC-READ-CNT
           END-IF
           .
